<!-- Title Page -->
<section id="title">
  <h1>Our Title</h1>
  <h2>Eyelens — See Clearly. Style Boldly.</h2>
  <p>
    Welcome to Eyelens — Where Vision Meets Style<br><br>
    At Eyelens, we believe that eyewear is not just an accessory — it’s an extension of who you are. Founded with a passion for redefining modern eyewear, Eyelens is dedicated to blending cutting-edge technology, superior craftsmanship, and timeless aesthetics to create eyewear that empowers confidence and elevates every look.<br><br>
    From classic aviators and chic cat-eye sunglasses to sleek blue-light blocking spectacles and precision-crafted prescription frames, our collection is meticulously curated to suit every lifestyle and personality. Each pair of Eyelens eyewear is designed using high-quality materials that offer durability, comfort, and optimal protection — whether it’s shielding your eyes from harmful UV rays, reducing glare, or minimizing blue light exposure from digital devices.<br><br>
    Driven by innovation and inspired by trends across the globe, Eyelens stands for quality, clarity, and individuality. We are committed to helping you see the world better — and letting the world see the best version of you.
  </p>
</section>

